          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Highway Restoration Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill provides for a phaseout of the Mass Transit Account by the end of FY2023. Beginning in FY2024, no funds would be transferred to the account from the Highway Trust Fund. </p>]]></text>
